data.meta_description: Check here U19 Allsvenskan results, fixtures, table and all relevant stats, from this season and all previous seasons.
data.text:
There are overall 14 teams that compete for the title every year.

The current holder of the title is IFK Norrköping U19 and the team that holds the most titles is IFK Göteborg U19.

Sofascore tracks live football scores and U19 Allsvenskan table, results, statistics and top scorers.

Which team in U19 Allsvenskan has the most titles?

The team with the most titles in U19 Allsvenskan is IFK Göteborg U19.

Which team is the current titleholder in U19 Allsvenskan?

The current titleholder in U19 Allsvenskan is IFK Norrköping U19.

How many goals are scored on average in U19 Allsvenskan in U19 Allsvenskan 2024?

The average number of goals in U19 Allsvenskan is 3.68.

When does the U19 Allsvenskan start and when does it finish?

The U19 Allsvenskan usually starts in March and ends in October.

How many groups are there in U19 Allsvenskan competition?

The teams in U19 Allsvenskan are placed in 6 groups.
